item.description:
All Important Meeting and Social to Kick off the 2010 Election Year. Newly formed groups will give updates on their progress, and lots of opportunities to jump in and get involved during the workshop session.

Let's take our state and our country back!

This will be agreat opportunity to meet and mingle with fellow Tea Party members. Cash bar and snacks will be available. The Quonset O Club is a great venue which can fit 350 people, so bring your friends and Let's Roll!


(from "RI" Tea party)
item.name: "RI" Tea Party January Open Meeting
